column1: Lean In: Women, Work, and the Will to Lead
Bobiverse 1: We Are Legion (We Are Bob)
column10: A standard 21st century software engineer nerd (Bob) dies young in a car accident. 100 years later he awakes to find that his conciousness has become the AI pilot of a space-faring drone whose mission it is to explore the cosmos for habitable planets and shepherd the human race off of a dying planet. Oh, and the fun part: he can clone himself.
The man who brought us Ready Player One (an ALL TIME fave) brought us a wholesome gamer coming-of-age story but with alien invasions.
